  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="heading">
        <head>Lily Of The Valley</head>
      </div>
      <div type="lyrics">
        <lg>
          <l>I am forever searching high and low</l>
          <l>But why does everybody tell me no</l>
          <l>Neptune of the seas</l>
          <l>Have you an answer for me please</l>
          <l>And the lily of the valley doesn't know</l>
        </lg>
        <lg>
          <l>I lie in wait with open eyes</l>
          <l>I carry on through stormy skies</l>
          <l>I follow every course</l>
          <l>My kingdom for a horse</l>
          <l>But each time I grow old</l>
          <l>Serpent of the Nile</l>
          <l>Relieve me for a while</l>
          <l>And cast me from your spell and let me go</l>
        </lg>
        <lg>
          <l>Messenger from Seven Seas has flown</l>
          <l>To tell the King of Rhye he's lost his throne</l>
          <l>Wars will never cease</l>
          <l>Is there time enough for peace</l>
          <l>But the lily of the valley doesn't know</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
